{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"sngth9ps6y3uky4x6k8zpbu","title":"Zsh","desc":"","updated":1662139490532,"created":1661057988414,"custom":{},"fname":"linux.customization.terminal.zsh","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"9b84045b66b93d27ae21f1f537a6aba6","links":[{"from":{"fname":"linux.customization.install-checklist","id":"6heqjju0cm02y0rjgk9kajk","vaultName":"docs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":7,"offset":473},"end":{"line":19,"column":43,"offset":509},"indent":[]},"value":"linux.customization.terminal.zsh"}],"anchors":{"install-zsh":{"type":"header","text":"Install zsh","value":"install-zsh","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"install-omz":{"type":"header","text":"Install Omz","value":"install-omz","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2},"config":{"type":"header","text":"Config","value":"config","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2},"themes":{"type":"header","text":"Themes","value":"themes","line":32,"column":0,"depth":3},"scripts--aliases":{"type":"header","text":"Scripts & Aliases","value":"scripts--aliases","line":36,"column":0,"depth":3},"completions":{"type":"header","text":"Completions","value":"completions","line":42,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"szoftx2gwbyhzholdig6yz2","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"zsh\">Zsh<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#zsh\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"install-zsh\">Install zsh<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install-zsh\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>through <a href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh\">oh my zsh</a></li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>sudo apt install zsh\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>change default shell <code>chsh -s $(which zsh)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"install-omz\">Install Omz<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install-omz\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh\">https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>sh -c \"$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)\"</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"config\">Config<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#config\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>the .omz folder is a git repository \n<ul>\n<li>Not suitable for creating soft link</li>\n<li>just creating soft link for neccesary files</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>.zshrc</code>: replacement for <code>.bashrc</code>\n<ul>\n<li>move additional commands from <code>bash.rc</code> -> <code>zsh.rc</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"themes\">Themes<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#themes\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>place custome theme <strong>files</strong> in <code>$HOME/.oh-my-zsh/custom/themes</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"scripts--aliases\">Scripts &#x26; Aliases<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#scripts--aliases\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>$HOME/.oh-my-zsh/custom</code></li>\n<li>each file must have the <code>.zsh</code> extension</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"completions\">Completions<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#completions\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>$HOME/.oh-my-zsh/completions</code></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/6heqjju0cm02y0rjgk9kajk\">Install Checklist</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children"